Class RangeConstraint<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.cq.social.ugc.api.AbstractConstraint
      • com.adobe.cq.social.ugc.api.AbstractPropertyConstraint
        • com.adobe.cq.social.ugc.api.RangeConstraint<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of object that is being queried.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constraint

    public class RangeConstraint<T>
extends AbstractPropertyConstraint
implements Constraint
    RangeConstraint is a property constraint which restricts the value of a property to a specific range.
